1
00:00:00,460 --> 00:00:05.560
Hello! Here you who are employed with sick pay can get help to apply for sickness benefit.

2
00:00:06,160 --> 00:00:11,080
Your employer must have been reported sick in order for you to make your application.

3
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:16,800
To be able to do your cases digitally, you need to have BankID -

4
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:20,020
And have logged in to My pages on insurance fund.se.

5
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:27,880
You can choose whether you want to apply for sickness benefit via computer, mobile phone or tablet.

6
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:33,920
The film describes how to do in eight steps that take about three minutes.

7
00:00:34,627 --> 00:00:38.307
Your application for sickness benefit is divided into three fields -

8
00:00:38,620 --> 00:00:45,080
My tasks, illness and medical certificates and scope and period.

9
00:00:45,460 --> 00:00:50,780
Click "Complete" to change the details in each field.

10
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:55,520
Click "Go On" to confirm your changes.

11
00:00:58,480 --> 00:01:04,000
Here you can see your personal and contact details. Make sure the information is correct.

12
00:01:07,940 --> 00:01:15,400
Here you can see employer information, information about income and work and account details.

13
00:01:15,746 --> 00:01:19,566
You need to provide current information about your work and your income.

14
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:23,220
You can find these in your employment contract.

15
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:27,360
You can also contact your employer for the right information.

16
00:01:29,373 --> 00:01:33,553
Fill in if you are back at work or if you are still on sick leave.

17
00:01:34,905 --> 00:01:41,425
If you or your doctor has not already submitted a medical certificate, you can choose to connect it now.

18
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:46,780
Here you describe what illness you have, what your work tasks look like -

19
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:50,080
And how you would have worked if you had been healthy.

20
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:54,820
Specify the extent to which you apply for sickness benefit.

21
00:01:56,008 --> 00:01:59.308
Now all three fields are filled and green marked.

22
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:04,700
Click in the check and approve box by signing with your BankID.

23
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:12,520
Once you have approved the application, you will receive a message that confirms that we have received your information.

24
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:15,700
Now you can follow your case on my pages.

25
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:19,680
Thank you for applying for sickness benefit via My pages!